rows.label: qev056002_MSG0002
rows.name:
We need you to head back to Cauldros and hunt 10
bio visigels with that weapon Han'barac gave you.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev056002_MSG0003
rows.name:
Doing so should put an end to their unnatural
multiplying.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev056002_MSG0004
rows.name:
Thanks for taking on such a dangerous mission.
That area is a little safer now because of you.[ST:wait ]
